comments: Harden (BKN) makes marginal contact to McDaniels' (MIN) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
McDaniels (MIN) makes slight contact with Harden's (BKN) body at the start of his drive and does not affect his SQBR as Harden loses control of the ball during his dribble.

call_type: Turnover: Lost Ball Out of Bounds
comments: Harden (BKN) dribbles the ball off his leg prior to it going out of bounds.
Green (BKN) legally contests Beasley (MIN) jump shot attempt.  Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.
Irving (BKN) cleanly dislodges the ball from Edwards (MIN) during the rebound.
Brown (BKN) reaches in and marginal contact occurs with Edwards' (MIN) arm during his shot attempt near the basket.
Edwards (MIN) cleanly deflects the ball from Brown (BKN) during his dribble at midcourt.
Brown (BKN) makes contact to Edwards' (MIN) body that affects his driving shot attempt.
Brown (BKN) briefly engages and disengages with Towns (MIN) during the rebound.
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Harris (BKN) and absorbs the contact.
